Project Description
DotSpatialApp is a UI wrapper around DotSpatial that includes a ribbon and docking panels. The functionality in this project is also be exposed as an extension package to MapWindow 6. Please download the release there.

The Ribbon and DockManager packages are published on the DotSpatial feed: www.myget.org/F/dotspatial/

 

This project is being archived and will be abandoned at the end of 2017
